[
    {
        "content": "<p>Hello, I currently work on creating an adequate abstraction for the crypto API.<br>\nTherefore I analyzed how hashing is performed in C (crypto_shash).<br>\nThe common way of hashing a value with a salt in C is calling <code>crypto_shash_init()</code> -&gt; <code>crypto_shash_update</code> (n times) -&gt; <code>crypto_shash_final</code>.<br>\nI added the <code>&lt;crypto/hash.h&gt;</code>header to the bindgen helpers to include.<br>\nI looked through the <a href=\"http://bindings_generated.rs\">bindings_generated.rs</a> and realized, that the function <a href=\"https://elixir.bootlin.com/linux/latest/source/include/crypto/hash.h#L940\"><code>crypto_shash_init()</code></a> is missing.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>extern &quot;C&quot; {\n    pub fn crypto_alloc_shash(\n        alg_name: *const c_types::c_char,\n        type_: u32_,\n        mask: u32_,\n    ) -&gt; *mut crypto_shash;\n}\nextern &quot;C&quot; {\n    pub fn crypto_shash_setkey(\n        tfm: *mut crypto_shash,\n        key: *const u8_,\n        keylen: c_types::c_uint,\n    ) -&gt; c_types::c_int;\n}\nextern &quot;C&quot; {\n    pub fn crypto_shash_digest(\n        desc: *mut shash_desc,\n        data: *const u8_,\n        len: c_types::c_uint,\n        out: *mut u8_,\n    ) -&gt; c_types::c_int;\n}\nextern &quot;C&quot; {\n    pub fn crypto_shash_tfm_digest(\n        tfm: *mut crypto_shash,\n        data: *const u8_,\n        len: c_types::c_uint,\n        out: *mut u8_,\n    ) -&gt; c_types::c_int;\n}\nextern &quot;C&quot; {\n    pub fn crypto_shash_update(\n        desc: *mut shash_desc,\n        data: *const u8_,\n        len: c_types::c_uint,\n    ) -&gt; c_types::c_int;\n}\nextern &quot;C&quot; {\n    pub fn crypto_shash_final(desc: *mut shash_desc, out: *mut u8_) -&gt; c_types::c_int;\n}\nextern &quot;C&quot; {\n    pub fn crypto_shash_finup(\n        desc: *mut shash_desc,\n        data: *const u8_,\n        len: c_types::c_uint,\n        out: *mut u8_,\n    ) -&gt; c_types::c_int;\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>How does it come that bindgen does not include all bindings?<br>\nAlso the function <a href=\"https://elixir.bootlin.com/linux/latest/source/include/crypto/hash.h#L732\"><code>crypto_free_shash</code></a> is missing.</p>",
        "id": 278659056,
        "sender_full_name": "Leon Gross",
        "timestamp": 1649750094
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"478998\">@Leon Gross</span> crypto_shash_init is static and inline. This means it doesn't end up being exported by any object file. For this reason bindgen skips it. You can add a wrapper function to the binding helpers called rust_crypto_shash_init and then call this function instead.</p>",
        "id": 278660569,
        "sender_full_name": "bjorn3",
        "timestamp": 1649751052
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"412316\">@bjorn3</span> thank you for your fast answer! This makes totally sense, I will do it like you proposed.</p>",
        "id": 278661070,
        "sender_full_name": "Leon Gross",
        "timestamp": 1649751406
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Hello, I'm trying to cherry-pick some changes from <code>rust</code> into <code>rust-next</code> and I'm having trouble understanding what causes the following error:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"err\">❯</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"cp\">$(</span><span class=\"n\">nproc</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">DESCEND</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">objtool</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">CALL</span><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">checksyscalls</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">sh</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>: <span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"na\">install_headers</span><span class=\"o\">'</span> <span class=\"nc\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">up</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">date</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">grep</span>: <span class=\"nc\">warning</span>: <span class=\"nc\">stray</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">\\</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">before</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>#\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">RUSTC</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">E0412</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>: <span class=\"nc\">cannot</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">find</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">type</span> <span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">scope</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">-</span>-&gt; <span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">home</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">amiculas</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">work</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bindings_helpers_generated</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>:<span class=\"mi\">69</span>:<span class=\"mi\">30</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">69</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">dget</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span>: <span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                              </span><span class=\"o\">^^^^^^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">found</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">scope</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">E0412</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>: <span class=\"nc\">cannot</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">find</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">type</span> <span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">scope</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">-</span>-&gt; <span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">home</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">amiculas</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">work</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bindings_helpers_generated</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span>:<span class=\"mi\">69</span>:<span class=\"mi\">46</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">69</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">dget</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span>: <span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                                              </span><span class=\"o\">^^^^^^</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">found</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">scope</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">error</span>: <span class=\"nc\">aborting</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">due</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">previous</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">errors</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">For</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">more</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">information</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">about</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kr\">try</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">rustc</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">explain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">E0412</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>: <span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span>:<span class=\"mi\">389</span>: <span class=\"nc\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bindings</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span>: <span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span>:<span class=\"mi\">1292</span>: <span class=\"nc\">prepare</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>What I'm backporting is a simple helper function:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">diff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">git</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">helpers</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">helpers</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span>\n<span class=\"n\">index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"n\">cb7b82053d8</span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"mi\">1623</span><span class=\"n\">dce9df1e</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">100644</span>\n<span class=\"o\">---</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">helpers</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+++</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">helpers</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span>\n<span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">25</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">25</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">7</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">@@</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span>#<span class=\"n\">include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">mutex</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span>#<span class=\"n\">include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">spinlock</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span>#<span class=\"n\">include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">sched</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">signal</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span>#<span class=\"n\">include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dcache</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__noreturn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">void</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rust_helper_BUG</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">void</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">121</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">6</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">122</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">12</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">@@</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">void</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rust_helper_put_task_struct</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">task_struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">EXPORT_SYMBOL_GPL</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rust_helper_put_task_struct</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">dentry</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">rust_helper_dget</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">dentry</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">       </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dget</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">dentry</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"n\">EXPORT_SYMBOL_GPL</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">rust_helper_dget</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span>\n<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cm\">/*</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  * We use `bindgen`'s `--size_t-is-usize` option to bind the C `size_t` type</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">  * as the Rust `usize` type, so we can use it in contexts where Rust</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>If anyone could point me in the right direction I would be grateful.</p>",
